del could be used as a part of a larger\nmalware detection system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 Oct 2018 02:02:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 21 Jun 2019 15:02:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-24"}
