me of the fluid, it can be shown that\nthe normal and magnetization current give one-third and two-thirds of the total\nCVE current respectively. This gives a natural solution to the 'one-third'\npuzzle in the CVE current in three-dimensional version of the chiral kinetic\ntheory in the literature.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 Oct 2018 02:25:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 17 Jun 2019 01:21:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-24"}
