ance compared to recent baselines of weakly\nsupervised methods. This paper can be seen as an application of image\ntranslation for cross domain object detection.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 Oct 2018 07:07:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-05"}
